  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/59634a57839eb35c3dcb087b2ad239d4.avif?t=1755275224\" width=617 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/981ab96bb0fc085ac24f1ac94eecb693.avif?t=1755275224\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accused of espionage against their own country, the pure and noble sisters Silas and Leila Nanashiel find themselves imprisoned without a fair trial. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leila gets sentenced to death for the alleged crime, her execution set to be carried out within merely a month. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only her sister Silas can save her from this fate, by breaking Leila out of prison. However, in order to gather information for their escape, Silas is forced to make deals with other prisoners and obey the guards’ harsh rule.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Though no matter what happens, she won’t give up. With the help of other inmates, the two sisters will reunite in freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/52314e1719b3f5085e7a09aab5bb6b85.avif?t=1755275224\" width=617 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/ca5ff2d6e33d87799bf1a26d13d71868.poster.avif?t=1755275224\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/ca5ff2d6e33d87799bf1a26d13d71868.webm?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/ca5ff2d6e33d87799bf1a26d13d71868.mp4?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/cd6e7e5b572f8fae33214437be384ab4.poster.avif?t=1755275224\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/cd6e7e5b572f8fae33214437be384ab4.webm?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/cd6e7e5b572f8fae33214437be384ab4.mp4?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/796ee23ac7432a7fdffe1f250c56d1a2.poster.avif?t=1755275224\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/796ee23ac7432a7fdffe1f250c56d1a2.webm?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/796ee23ac7432a7fdffe1f250c56d1a2.mp4?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/d8cc6e80c0532c42c7c25d61bf1448cc.poster.avif?t=1755275224\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/d8cc6e80c0532c42c7c25d61bf1448cc.webm?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/d8cc6e80