ass=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/b2263b065f7677c59ceb1a0cd05667d1.avif?t=1755275224\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Silas, beautiful daughter of an aristocratic family imprisoned in the lawless ‘Otar Prison’. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain information inside the prison and gather the seven jailbreakers to plot the breakout. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/aa8472751dceff1622350db68ffcaa94.avif?t=1755275224\" width=617 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/474b3c89ac7f365e293d38e94f225712.poster.avif?t=1755275224\" width=350 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/474b3c89ac7f365e293d38e94f225712.webm?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836340/extras/474b3c89ac7f365e293d38e94f225712.mp4?t=1755275224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live2d animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic expressions: Based on mood and story progression, Silas and the other girls showcase a broad array of emotions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long story spanning across several chapters as you meet more characters and progress the escape plan.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 save slots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A detailed minimap and fast travel feature for ease of navigation.</p></li></ul>",
